Not yet. I wanted to see if this was happening to anyone else, in case betfair just reply with the stock reply "clear your cache".

So, is anyone actually using RUNNER_METADATA? If yes can you test it for Saturday (14-May-22) racing? Take a look at the 1:35 Newbury race->Cadamosto. The horse is missing the BRED code (should be IRE), the OWNER_NAME is missing 'rg' off westerberg, the SIRE_NAME,DAM_NAME,DAMSIRE_NAME and the corresponding BREDs are missing!
